social_posts.post_text: When we moved into our new place, our aim was to maintain a minimalist and clutter-free environment. However, we knew we needed a standout piece, and that’s where the Belia sectional sofa from @roveconcepts came in. With its sleek curves, low profile, and spacious seating area, the Belia effortlessly combines support and coziness. To complement the sofa, we also acquired the Kara coffee table from Rove Concepts, completing the perfect setup for a relaxing atmosphere #RefinedLuxuryLiving [AD]

Timeless elegance at its finest. These classic watches embody the essence of sophistication and style. From the iconic @rolex Precision to the legendary @omega Speedmaster Professional and the exquisite @cartier Tank Francaise, they are more than just timekeepers – they are statements of enduring fashion. In a world where trends come and go, investing in a watch that never goes out of style is a mark of true refinement. These timepieces stand the test of time, serving as reminders that true beauty is eternal.

Video by @chris.bellizzi

Head to toe in the new Spring/Summer ‘23 collection from @hockerty.men. For those unfamiliar, Hockerty specializes in creating custom made clothing for the modern man. With a focus on impeccable craftsmanship and personalized style, they offer tailored suits, shirts, and accessories. Definitely a brand you should have on your radar.
I’ve always been a morning person. How about you?

Wedding season is in full swing, and if you’re still looking for that perfect tux, then @sayki1924 has you covered. Check out their incredible selection and Memorial Day sale happening right now. #YouHaveMoreToShow
The timeless polo shirt by @sayki1924. This is a summer staple for me and Sayki nails it with their lightweight and breathable take of this classic shirt. #YouHaveMoreToShow

I had the pleasure of experiencing an absolutely unforgettable weekend at the @veuveclicquot Polo Classic, an event that unofficially ushers in the arrival of summer. This year's edition, the first one since 2019, surpassed all previous ones. 

The joy of reuniting with friends from various corners of the country was immeasurable, and the bonds formed with new acquaintances were equally delightful. Till next time! #VCPoloClassic #VeuveClicquot #VeuveCliquotPoloClassic

This past Saturday, we had a lovely time at the 2023 Summer Party presented by @maxmara, supported by @victorinox, at the Glass House campus in New Canaan, Connecticut. The event was fantastic, offering exploration, entertainment, a delicious picnic lunch, performances, and refreshing cocktails from @hennessy Paradis on the lawn. The day also celebrated the debut of exclusive artwork by @derrickadamsny. 

Thank you @battalion_pr for a great day!

During my recent visit to the @piombofficial store in Soho, I had the opportunity to handpick some standout pieces. The blazer, pants, and denim shirt I’m wearing here caught my attention and perfectly compliment each other. To complete the look, I chose the incredibly comfortable Lex Beige Nubuck loafers from @jacquessoloviereparis and pair of sunglasses from @orlebarbrown.

I recently had the pleasure of visiting @jectnyc for a consultation and a quick treatment, and I must say, it was one of the most exceptional spa experiences I’ve ever had. From the moment I walked in, the friendly staff made me feel welcome, and the facility’s clean and beautiful design added to the overall pleasant ambiance. My provider, @morganking.pa, demonstrated an impressive level of expertise, meticulousness, and a delightful demeanor - I appreciate you! If you’re looking to enhance your skincare routine, I wholeheartedly recommend JECT. Also, they’re currently offering a fantastic deal with the code MKACAR20, which grants first-time appointments a generous 20% discount!

Opting for the classic chino/oxford look with a sweater tied around the neck, I found the chinos to be incredibly comfortable and maintaining their appearance even after a full day of wear. Knowing it would serve as the centerpiece of the look, I carefully selected understated elements to complement it. I decided to bring out my glen check tan suit from @indochino, which had been sitting in my closet untouched for over two years - I had designed it with patch pockets, intending for it to be worn casually. To complement the suit, I paired it with a lightweight button-down shirt from @etonshirts and completed the ensemble with stylish Hoyt monk straps from @beckettsimonon. As a sentimental touch, I adorned my father's special army watch, a token of appreciation for his service in the Turkish military.

Excited to collaborate with @beckettsimonon and showcase their Hoyt Monstraps styled in two different ways. For those who may not be familiar with the brand, Beckett Simonon is a direct-to-consumer company renowned for its exquisite, handcrafted footwear and accessories. Their core values revolve around delivering exceptional quality, promoting sustainability, and maintaining affordability. Achieving this, they adopt a unique approach by manufacturing in small batches and offering pre-orders, effectively bypassing traditional retail markups. [AD]

One of the highlights of my recent visit to Istanbul a couple of weeks ago with @turkishairlines was attending the Turkish Airlines World Golf Cup tournament as a guest of the airline at the stunning Kemer Country Club. This event is an annual corporate amateur golf tournament initiated by Turkish Airlines in 2013. The winners from global qualifiers gather at a Grand Final held in Belek, Turkey, during the same week as the Turkish Airlines Open.

Thank you to the entire team for your exceptional hospitality throughout the memorable event. #TurkishAirlines #WorldGolfCup2023 #IstanbulTournament

What if you could enjoy specialty coffee at home, without sacrificing quality or convenience?

That’s exactly what @xbloom_coffee does. This award-winning pour-over machine, brings the expertise of your favorite roaster and barista right to your kitchen. It’s designed for coffee enthusiasts and those seeking exceptional coffee experiences.

XBloom is super intuitive to use - just scan the pod, pour water, and tap. It’s the closest thing to getting a pour-over from your favorite cafe, but with the convenience of a pod machine. 

xBloom replicates the pour-over mastery of renowned cafes like Stumptown, transforming anyone into a coffee connoisseur. Whether a seasoned aficionado or a budding enthusiast, xBloom elevates your coffee journey. #xBloomcoffee #FindTheCoffeeConnoisseurInYou #GetxBloom

When I acquired this beautiful vintage Zegna suit, I knew I needed to find a trustworthy tailor to make the necessary adjustments. That's where @alteration_specialists came in. With 12 locations throughout NYC, Alteration Specialists offer high-quality custom tailoring services to meet your tailoring needs. From their elite-level customer service to their incredibly skilled tailors, they get an A+ from me. Stay tuned for the final look!

A great way to spend Sunday! I finally had the chance to read “Monday to Sunday Istanbul,” a beautifully crafted book gifted to me by Sinan Sokmen, the co-author, a couple of months ago during my visit to Istanbul. Sinan and his wife, Seda Domanic, did such an amazing job jam packed with information. The book presents a week of curated experiences in Istanbul. The book invites readers to follow carefully selected itineraries for each day of the week, perfectly matched with the specific time of day. Then, leading local figures - famous chefs, artists, documentary makers, academics, designers, journalists, entrepreneurs and architects - share their insights into their hometown.
